      "markText": "有人说，时间像一条忘旧河，但到远方换换空气也好像在忘旧河里喝一口水；尽管它起的作用没有那么厉害，但发作起来却更快。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2049&rangeEnd=2293",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2049&rangeEnd=2293"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_7_1804-1890",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1804-1890",
      "markText": "这位青年人涉世未深，两天的旅程就把他跟过去的世界隔得远远的，所有称之为责任、志趣、烦恼、前途等种种意识，他都置之脑后；这种远离尘嚣之感，远远比他坐马车到火车站去时来得强烈。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1804&rangeEnd=1890",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1804&rangeEnd=1890"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_11_5904-6001",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "5904-6001",
      "markText": "不论是谁，工作都该是他无条件地最最值得尊重的东西，除了工作之外，基本上没有别的更值得重视了。它是人们立身的准则，它关系到一个人的成败。这在时间上也有绝对性的意义，也可以说，它种瓜得瓜，种豆得豆。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=5904&rangeEnd=6001",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=5904&rangeEnd=6001"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_26_4130-4192",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "4130-4192",
      "markText": "于是克罗科夫斯基大夫说了出来：它是以疾病的形态重新出现的！疾病的症状，是情欲乔装打扮的活动形态，而所有的疾病都是变相的情欲。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=4130&rangeEnd=4192",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=4130&rangeEnd=4192"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_14_4889-4960",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "4889-4960",
      "markText": "生病和死亡其实没有什么了不起，它们不过是混日子的一种方式。只有山下人才一本正经地对待生活。我想只要你在山上住得久些，你迟早会懂得这个道理的。”",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=4889&rangeEnd=4960",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=4889&rangeEnd=4960"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_8_3078-3136",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3078-3136",
      "markText": "这是一种奄奄无生气的咳嗽，它不是阵发性的，而像有某种有机溶液的稠黏物质一阵阵无力而令人憎嫌地泛上来，发出咯咯的声音。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3078&rangeEnd=3136",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3078&rangeEnd=3136"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_6_806-859",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "806-859",
      "markText": "它时间上比讲故事的年代早得多，它的年份不能用日子计算，它所贯穿的时间究竟有多长，也无法用太阳的出没来衡量。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=806&rangeEnd=859",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=806&rangeEnd=859"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_7_3101-3165",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3101-3165",
      "markText": "火车有时在寒碜的小车站前、有时在大车站前停下来，朝着相反的方向离去，使人摸不清究竟往哪儿行驶，再也记不起自己在天涯的哪一个角落。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3101&rangeEnd=3165",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3101&rangeEnd=3165"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_21_6480-6514",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "6480-6514",
      "markText": "人们认为，笨人必然健康而平凡，而疾病则能使人变得高雅聪明，超脱不群。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=6480&rangeEnd=6514",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=6480&rangeEnd=6514"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_7_4011-4083",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4011-4083",
      "markText": "他们重逢时并没有热情洋溢的表示，这在头脑冷静的人们中间往往有这种习惯。说也奇怪，他们之间彼此一直不喊名字，仅仅是为了不使内心热烈的真情流露出来。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4011&rangeEnd=4083",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4011&rangeEnd=4083"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_11_4003-4043",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "4003-4043",
      "markText": "人们不仅仅以个人的身份生活，而是不知不觉地与他的时代和同时代的人同呼吸，共命运。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4003&rangeEnd=4043",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4003&rangeEnd=4043"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_47_29672-29735",
      "chapterUid": 47,
      "range": "29672-29735",
      "markText": "人类的尊严和高贵寓于精神，也就是寓于疾病；一言以蔽之，一个人越是多病，他就越是高度发展的人，疾病的天才比健康的天才更富有人性。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=47&rangeStart=29672&rangeEnd=29735",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=47&rangeStart=29672&rangeEnd=29735"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_5_2226-2294",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2226-2294",
      "markText": "数年后肖夏太太回疗养院，身边伴着的是荷兰富商皮佩尔科尔恩，这不由使汉斯·卡斯托尔普妒火中烧，但经过一番波折，这三个人终于结成亲密的友谊。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2226&rangeEnd=2294",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2226&rangeEnd=2294"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_58_27686-27760",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "27686-27760",
      "markText": "“胆小鬼！”纳夫塔尖叫一声。在这声人性的叫喊中，他承认开枪打别人比挨别人的枪需要更大的勇气。他把手枪握成了与决斗无涉的姿势，往自己的脑袋上开了一枪。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=27686&rangeEnd=27760",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=27686&rangeEnd=27760"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_39_36165-36234",
      "chapterUid": 39,
      "range": "36165-36234",
      "markText": "——“不外是对你的一种爱慕。不错，在我的眼睛一接触到你的瞬间，或者说当我认识你后，我就爱上你了——很明显，是爱情把我引到这块地方来的……”",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=39&rangeStart=36165&rangeEnd=36234",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=39&rangeStart=36165&rangeEnd=36234"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_7_479-700",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "479-700",
      "markText": "一位纯朴的青年在盛夏时节从家乡汉堡出发，到格劳宾迪申的达沃斯高地旅行。他准备乘车作为期三周的访问。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=479&rangeEnd=700",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=479&rangeEnd=700"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_10_5817-5873",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5817-5873",
      "markText": "做孩子和孙子的往往先观摩，而后产生景仰之心，再由景仰而萌生学习之念，并从先代遗传下来的素质中培育出自己的个性来。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5817&rangeEnd=5873",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5817&rangeEnd=5873"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_7_5558-5645",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5558-5645",
      "markText": "“他们在这儿把人类的时间当儿戏，这点你压根儿不会相信。在他们看来，三星期好比一天。你不久就可以亲眼目睹，把一切看得一清二楚，”他又接下去说，“这儿，人们对事物的概念改变了。”",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25118042&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5558&rangeEnd=5645",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2e832370717f455a2e84fa7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5558&rangeEnd=5645"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25118042_10_8991-9070",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "8991-9070",
      "markText": "所有这一切，特别是这么多的晚香玉，无非都说明死既不美丽动人，也根本不用伤心，而是一种几乎是不体面的、涉及血肉之躯的事，应当掩饰，应当遗忘，而不该常常记在心里。",
